<div class="tab-copy">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>This tab is the default selected partial. It is rendered by <code>{{ "{{ selection }}" }}</code> when no selection header is present.</p>
    <ul>
        <li>The page shell remains stable.</li>
        <li>The content panel is server-rendered.</li>
        <li>The active tab is derived from the request selection.</li>
    </ul>
</div>
